dct_description_sm: A set of digitized microfilm of manuscript maps of Iowa townships. Individual maps in the set may include: Native American villages and fields; the first farmsteads, town sites and fields established by settlers; networks of trails; distribution of rivers, woods, prairies, wetlands and springs; and survey data such as creator, date created, and date accepted.
dct_rights_sm: Material in the public domain. No restrictions on use. For  more information, contact the University of Iowa Libraries Map Collection: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact.
